articles.title: NASA, Lockheed Martin reveal subtly supersonic X-59 plane - The Register
articles.description: Boffins say the quiet part out loud: There's no room for the sonic boom
articles.content:
NASA's X-59 quiet supersonic aircraft made its public debut on Friday in a media event at the Lockheed Martin Skunk Works in Palmdale, California, where the plane was designed.
